column5: I have had a great year,and met a bunch of good folks from OFC.Some got me out of a jam.Some joined me in outings.All was good and all were great.I wish everyone a merry xmass and a happy new year.cheers and esp a vey merry xmass to the admins.cheers vince
And a Merry Christmas and Happy New Year to you Vince...Glad you like the company here
I do,there are a great bunch here and problably more that may waunder in.
Thanks, Vince, glad to hear that you like it round these here parts.  Somehow, we mostly collect really very fine folks.  God Bless you and your family this Christmas season.

thank you sir,and to you as well.best wishs to you and your family this holiday season.Im waiting up for santa tonight,well i will try anyway.A glass of milk with cookies and maybe a teaser in the milk.
